    "data with a cosine similarity exceeding this threshold are grouped into the same class, whereas text data falling below the threshold are classified as unclustered, resulting in the identification of distinct file categories.",
    "Next, data from the clustered files are extracted based on a 10% upward rounding ratio.",
    "These extracted data are ultimately merged with the unclustered data to construct a comprehensive clustered dataset.",
    "In the context of data clustering, 3,933 locomotive maintenance data entries are extracted from the expanded dataset.",
